[SN]TITLE[SN]
Bafta Cymru Games Awards winners announced in Cardiff

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Rantmedia took the top prize at the Bafta Cymru Games Awards.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
It won best game for TV Sports Soccer at a ceremony at the Tramshed in Cardiff on Saturday.
Thud Media won three commendations for artistic achievement, gameplay design and sound and music for children's educational game Boj Smoothies.
Director of Bafta Cymru, Hannah Raybould, said: "We are very proud to support the growing games industry in Wales."
Cube Kids scooped the technical achievement commendation for Teletubbies.
